	<h1 class="title">为了和科技公司竞争，汽车公司们要烧钱了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/3910/small/3910.png?1418028195" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">唐怡园 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-12 08:02:14 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/18917/medium/18917.jpg?1449813737" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


